    <string name="crash_report_instructions">Help improve Clint by reporting bugs on GitHub. No data is sent automatically — you choose what to share.</string>
    <string name="crash_steps_title">How to file a report</string>
    <string name="crash_steps">1. Reproduce the crash or bug\n2. Return here and tap the crash entry to expand it\n3. Tap the copy icon to copy the crash log\n4. Tap \"Open GitHub Issues\" below\n5. Click \"New issue\" on GitHub\n6. Copy the template below, paste it, and attach your crash log\n7. Fill in the steps that caused the crash and submit</string>
